item.title: Chapter 2-6: Android Head Units
item.description: The local car accessory market has been an upsurge in more affordbale Android car head units which varry from Ksh.5000 upto Ksh.20,000. These devices offer the same Android experience as a mobile device hence user experience really needs no re-learning. The brand names varry as well and some really have no specific brands. Online stores locally will mark them as Generic 2DIN 9.0‚Äù Android 8.x Car Stereo Radio MP5 Player. The MP5 mention is just as amusing to say the least.
